    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy. This car is in truly stunning condition\u2014honestly, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been pampered since day one, always garage-kept, and is looking for a new home where it\u2019ll be just as loved. You won't find a single blemish on it! Come take a look, you\u2019re going to fall in love the moment you see it. \u2728",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
