      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an exceptional 2011 Porsche 911 Carrera S (997.2), a pinnacle of mechanical purity. This specimen features the 3.8L Direct Fuel Injection (DFI) flat-six, providing a broad torque curve and immediate throttle response. The 6-speed manual gearbox is paired with a factory Limited Slip Differential (LSD), ensuring tactile feedback and superior power delivery. Equipped with Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM), the chassis remains perfectly composed under high lateral G-loads. The braking system features four-piston monobloc calipers and cross-drilled rotors with zero thermal stress. A recent DME report confirms no over-revs, and the underbody remains factory-sealed with no fluid seepage. This is a turn-key, investment-grade example for the driver who prioritizes structural rigidity and drivetrain integrity.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Mint condition. Clean title. No accidents. Full service history. Garage kept. Non-smoker. No mechanical issues.",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
