    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, collector-grade vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it rolled off the showroom floor. This car has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment, and the deep, mirror-like finish of the exterior paint is entirely free of swirls, chips, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains pristine; the premium leather upholstery shows zero bolster wear, and the original 'new car' scent persists. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the climate control, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, this vehicle is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive service history documenting preventative maintenance performed well ahead of manufacturer recommendations. With a recently applied ceramic coating and a spotless undercarriage, this is a rare opportunity to own a turn-key masterpiece that satisfies even the most discerning eye.",
      "price": 48900.0,
