    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presented in showroom-grade condition, this vehicle represents an uncompromising standard of automotive excellence. Every surface, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior, has been meticulously preserved to satisfy the most discerning collector. Mechanically peerless and aesthetically indistinguishable from new, this unit offers a rare opportunity to acquire a benchmark example of its class. We invite serious inquiries for this investment-grade acquisition.",
