    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, it\u2019s a total gem. You won't find another one in this kind of shape\u2014it\u2019s basically like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been pampered in a garage and drives like a total dream. If you're looking for something that feels brand new and has been loved every mile of the way, this is the one for you. Come take it for a spin, you'll fall in love instantly!",
      "price": 44900.0,
